318
00:19:47.290 --> 00:19:49.880
The day we reached the final island,

319
00:19:50.460 --> 00:19:53.510
we learned everything about the world.

320
00:19:58.010 --> 00:20:00.600
We uncovered the mysteries
of the Void Century...

321
00:20:00.600 --> 00:20:02.930
the people of the D...

322
00:20:02.930 --> 00:20:04.890
and the ancient weapons.

323
00:20:05.390 --> 00:20:09.230
We also learned Wano's
borders were once open.

324
00:20:07.500 --> 00:20:14.550
♪ As a kid, I had a dream ♪
♪ of a dazzling treasure ♪

325
00:20:14.550 --> 00:20:21.830
♪ I had a map in my head ♪
♪ that I knew would lead me ♪

326
00:20:15.610 --> 00:20:19.200
When we laid our eyes upon
that extraordinary treasure...

327
00:20:21.580 --> 00:20:23.450
all Roger could do...

328
00:20:21.830 --> 00:20:28.290
♪ Charted a course all on my own, ♪
♪ so nobody would beat me ♪

329
00:20:25.580 --> 00:20:26.910
was laugh.

330
00:20:28.710 --> 00:20:30.710
So did we!

331
00:20:29.040 --> 00:20:36.340
♪ The promised land was in my hand ♪
♪ drew a line in the sand ♪

332
00:20:30.710 --> 00:20:33.420
We laughed until tears
streamed down our faces!

333
00:20:38.970 --> 00:20:41.800
♪ Day after day ♪

334
00:20:43.720 --> 00:20:48.810
♪ Billowing dust is filling all my daydreams ♪

335
00:20:47.600 --> 00:20:50.350
Oh, Joyboy, how I wish...

336
00:20:48.810 --> 00:20:53.110
♪ There will come a time ♪

337
00:20:50.980 --> 00:20:54.570
that I could have lived in the same era as you.

338
00:20:53.110 --> 00:20:58.110
♪ Yeah, in the end ♪

339
00:20:56.610 --> 00:20:59.950
How could you leave this
stupendous treasure?!

340
00:20:58.110 --> 00:21:04.830
♪  It will be nothing but a fading echo ♪

341
00:21:00.360 --> 00:21:02.950
A tale full of laughter...

342
00:21:04.830 --> 00:21:11.960
♪ But if the world ever changes ♪
♪ I'll call out your name ♪

343
00:21:07.580 --> 00:21:09.290
Hey, everyone...

344
00:21:10.330 --> 00:21:15.800
We're the first people to reach this final island
in 800 years. Why don't we give it a name?

345
00:21:11.960 --> 00:21:18.760
♪ We could return to a time ♪
♪ when our lives were still the same ♪

346
00:21:15.800 --> 00:21:18.760
Let's call it...

347
00:21:19.170 --> 00:21:26.100
♪ Take me to the place where memories remain ♪

348
00:21:26.100 --> 00:21:33.980
♪ Please don't ever let them fade ♪

349
00:21:28.980 --> 00:21:30.600
Laugh Tale!
